item.title: Lance Parrish, Author Jerry Izenberg
item.description:
Host Bill Donohue welcomes former Detroit Tigers catcher Lance Parrish and later talks with Jerry Izenberg, author of the new book Larry Doby in Black and White: The Story of a Baseball Pioneer.

Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/sports-talk-new-york/

item.title: Cliff Notes: MONETIZING YOUR AUDIENCE
item.description:
Cam Kirk shares his unique approach to expanding his photography career using a music artist's formula. Learn how Cam leveraged his following to create Camp Kirk Studios, a physical space serving the Atlanta community, and his plans for global expansion.

Learn how he monetizes his brand beyond just fan support, turning it into a multi-faceted empire... Feed: https://feeds.redcircle.com/d11aeaba-b834-4b42-986d-6f9ef00d715f
